appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This release includes new features, bug fixes, and performance improvements.
New:
- You can now reorder your media downloads to listen in the order you want.
- Media search has been removed from the app header and is now in the left navigation menu.
Improved:
- Messaging now loads faster!
- Better support for Subsplash Live.
Fixed:
- Fixed several issues where push notifications were not opening Messaging correctly.
- Fixed issue where messages were appearing in the wrong channel.

title: PastorPaul.net

creator: Subsplash Inc
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the official Destined for Victory app! This app features powerful teaching from Pastor Paul Sheppard designed to strengthen and encourage you in your walk with Christ.

Destined for Victory is the broadcast ministry of Pastor Paul Sheppard. With a love for laughter and tell-it-like-it-is approach, Pastor Paul shares biblical truth in a down-to-earth way that anyone can understand. App features include:

*Free, on-demand access to the Destined for Victory program
*New broadcasts every weekday
*Recent sermon archives
*Download feature for all sermons
*Note-taking capability
*In-app Bible and Bible reading plans
*Easy access to online giving
*and more!

Strengthen your walk with God with practical teaching on-the-go. Get ready to live a life of victory and download our app today!

The Destined for Victory app was developed with the Subsplash App Platform.
descriptionShort: Destined for Victory with Pastor Paul Sheppard gives you timeless truth for life
